    Basic Scan: Scan all ports, run a generic vulnerability script.
    Command: sudo nmap -p- --script vuln 10.0.0.85

    Enhanced Scan: Scan, use specific vuln scripts for deeper analysis.
    Command: sudo nmap -p- --script vulners,http-vuln-* 10.0.0.85

    Thorough Scan: In-depth scan, including version detection and vulnerability checks.
    Command: sudo nmap -p- -sV --script vuln,exploit 10.0.0.85

    Comprehensive Scan: Extensive scan with OS detection, version, and vulnerability checks.
    Command: sudo nmap -p- -sV -A --script=default,exploit,vuln,safe 10.0.0.85
